text: Erik Rylander (3 September 1905 - 9 September 1976) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1932 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:1976 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1932 Winter Olympics Category:People from Falun
